*/* EYE CATCHER: EPIE                                                */ 00875000
*/* OFFSET: X'0'                                                     */ 00900000
*/* LENGTH: 4                                                        */ 00925000
*/*                                                                  */ 00950000
*/* STORAGE ATTRIBUTES:                                              */ 00975000
*/*  SUBPOOL:  130 or 250                                            */ 01000000
*/*  KEY:  TCB Key                                                   */ 01025000
*/*                                                                  */ 01050000
*/* SIZE: 160 bytes                                                  */ 01075000
*/*                                                                  */ 01100000
*/* CREATED BY: IEAVTESP                                             */ 01125000
*/*                                                                  */ 01150000
*/* POINTED TO BY:                                                   */ 01175000
*/*     Register 1 upon entry to an ESPIE exit routine.  The EPIE    */ 01193700
*/*     can also be found via SCAPIE + 32 (The EPIE immediately      */ 01212400
*/*     follows the PIE in storage).                             @P2C*/ 01231200
*/*                                                                  */ 01250000
*/* SERIALIZATION: Task Active                                       */ 01275000
*/*                                                                  */ 01300000
*/* FUNCTION:                                                        */ 01325000
*/*     The EPIE is used to pass program interruption information    */ 01350000
*/*     to an ESPIE exit routine.                                    */ 01375000
*/*                                                                  */ 01400000
*/* METHOD OF ACCESS:                                                */ 01425000
*/* ASM:                                                             */ 01450000
*/*            IHAEPIE                                               */ 01475000
*/*                                                                  */ 01500000
*/* PLS:                                                             */ 01525000
*/*           DCL EPIEPTR PTR                                        */ 01550000
*/*           %INCLUDE SYSLIB(IHAEPIE)                               */ 01575000
*/*                                                                  */ 01600000
*/*                                                                  */ 01675000
*/* CHANGE ACTIVITY:                                                 */ 01700000
*/*     $01 = OY21512  HBB3310 890401 PDCK: PASS ARS                 */ 01725000
*/*     $02 = OY36454  HBB4410 901015 PDCK: ESPIE RETRY MODE         */ 01750000
*/*     $P1 = PIG2274  HBB5510 930806 PDKD: SHOWHDR                  */ 01775000
*/*$P2=PN70102  HBB5520 940106 PD16KD: Update 'POINTED TO BY'    @P2A*/ 01787500
*/*$P3=PN70279  HBB5520 940307 PDKD: Provide more field granularity  */ 01791600
*/*                                  no version change needed    @P3A*/ 01795700
*/*$P4=PR20011  HBB6601 950908 PDKD: SC1CM compid split          @P4A*/ 01797800
*/*$L1=IEEERTM  HBB6606 970807 PDXB: DXC                             */ 01798900
